Sharif argues that celebrities could make as just much of an impact, if not more, by traveling to Russia for premieres and other business, and speaking out about its laws. "If you're actually allies in the community, go there and take a stand," he says, adding that by doing so, they can bring more attention to the issue, both here and in Russia.
